examples.text: Dil Devrimi döneminde Fransızca, Farsça ve Arapçadan bir sürü yeni sözcük öykünülmüştü. Bu ise yapılan hatalardan biriydi.
examples.translation: During the language revolution, lots of neologisms were calqued from French, Persian and Arabic. And this was one of the mistakes that were done.

etymology: From Proto-Turkic *ödkün- (“to imitate”), cognate with Yakut үтүгүн (ütügün, “to imitate”).
